title: The Throne of Zeus - Choose Your Own Adventure 40.pdf
description:
The Throne of Zeus, by Deborah Lerme Goodman, is the 40th book published in the series of Choose Your Own Adventure books.

This particular book was published in January 1985, close to 30 years ago.  Being able to digitize it and "re-publish" this book on tpb three decades later is neat.

I've been collecting these books myself, since I was a young child, and some of my fondest memories are of getting these books, at quality bookstores.

Enjoy!
